description_html:
A continuous solid wood filament that can be looped to create a one, two, or three seated bench.

Two loops create one seat: W29", D18.75", H18", SD18.75", SH18"
Five loops create two seats: W58.5", D18.75", H18", SD18.75", SH18"
Seven loops create three seats: W78.5", D18.75", H18", SD18.75", SH18"
